        When Your Brisbane Property Passes In at Auction: What Sellers Should Do Next
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Passing in is not the result you wanted, but it is not a failed sale. The decisions made in the hours immediately after the auction will determine what happens next.
